{"tid":2253574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook 監控屏蔽團隊大多數是持H-1B簽證的中國人","createTime":"2020-10-22T08:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:35:18.000Z","uid":294518,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5df42d8356353e8fb77db4cfde8888b448c5affe","tid":2253574,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:50:14.000Z","msg":"Facebook 監控屏蔽團隊大多數是持H-1B簽證的中國人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMeet your (Chinese) Facebook censors<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2020/10/20/meet-your-chinese-facebook-censors/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F10%2F20%2Fmeet-your-chinese-facebook-censors%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=999a3ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2020/10/20/meet-your-chinese-facebook-censors/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NOUHZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NOUHZF.png&h=a4358418&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"825e66314679ee760d5efe1371aa03d3dd83747d","tid":2253574,"uid":33874,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"H-1B簽證是美國簽發給在該國從事專業技術類工作的人士的簽證，屬於非移民簽證，是美國最主要的工作簽證類別。這種簽證必須由僱主出面為申請人申請，且申請人的雇用申請書需要美國公民及移民服務局的批准。每年H-1B簽證發放85000個名額，其中20000個優先名額屬於研究生或研究生以上學歷的受益人申請，而另外65000個名額則屬於本科生或者沒有獲取優先名額的其他受益人獲取。"},{"pid":"4d551e2b057448d3717ceadb8604406203aa2b92","tid":2253574,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2973cffabc8673ec3eab8e0ebd